%A1c-L%E1%BB%99c-s%C6%A1n-%C4%90%E1%BA%A1o-L%C3%A2m-nh%E1%BB%8B-t%E1%BB%B1-h%C3%A0nh/poem-O_hvcU6i1bycqcN57EcRNg">Nhạc Lộc sơn Đạo Lâm nhị tự hành - 岳麓山道林二寺行</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/author-Se3x2jWTezvoDpkpSU9qjg">Đỗ Phủ</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/T%C3%B9ng-Thi%E1%BB%87n-V%C6%B0%C6%A1ng/Qu%C3%A1-Vi%C3%AAn-Gi%C3%A1c-t%E1%BB%B1/poem-OBilrGMDCu4hSTBaNdpzlQ">Quá Viên Giác tự - 過圓覺寺</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/T%C3%B9ng-Thi%E1%BB%87n-V%C6%B0%C6%A1ng/author-ZzgazbvW_31Yn18OxsV6nA">Tùng Thiện Vương</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-%C4%90%E1%BB%A9c-%C4%90%E1%BA%A1t/Tr%C3%BA-ngo%E1%BA%A1-v%C4%83n-t%E1%BB%B1-t%C4%83ng-thuy%E1%BA%BFt-kinh/poem-KYpNc38SzaJzfhWDL56kPQ">Trú ngoạ văn tự tăng thuyết kinh - 晝臥聞寺僧説經</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-%C4%90%E1%BB%A9c-%C4%90%E1%BA%A1t/author-QedIvlr4BuYMTZh_TuTCTA">Nguyễn Đức Đạt</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C3%BD-Th%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-%E1%BA%A8n/T%C3%BAc-T%E1%BA%A5n-X%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-%C4%91%C3%ACnh-v%C4%83n-kinh-c%E1%BA%A7m/poem-Sn2sk9eRGKK2CrxOPFSpbQ">Túc Tấn Xương đình văn kinh cầm - 宿晉昌亭聞驚禽</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C3%BD-Th%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-%E1%BA%A8n/author-9iJ5oLtFQBkuT0Ej5xvn9Q">Lý Thương Ẩn</a>)<br></div>	</div>
